data.description: Discover your dream townhome nestled in the heart of Victoria Park - an idyllic haven for both living and leisure. Meticulously updated with a discerning designer's touch, this residence boasts a chef's kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances, lustrous quartz countertops, and elegant brass gold accents. This haven offers three inviting terraces plus a private rooftop retreat, ideal for entertaining or relaxing. The versatile third-level "den" serves as a perfect home office, creating a seamless work-from-home experience. Convenience is paramount, with the Galleria Mall just a stroll away, Las Olas within a mile, and the ocean's beauty a mere 1.2 miles from your doorstep. Seeing is believing – prepare to be captivated by the sheer splendor of this home!
